                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.51/935: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bundy</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-05-20T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 20, 1919, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your May 12, 5 p.m.</p>
                <p>In view of loan negotiations and affairs affecting Liberia now under
                    consideration in Paris, suggest Liberian Government defer commissioning French
                    customs receiver until definite plans for the proposed rehabilitation of Liberia
                    are concluded.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
